data.description: CO living at its best! Welcome home to the magical setting of Lakemoor West, a well kept secret. Your new home sits on over 13 acres of tree and rock formation land, that backs to BLM land, with Four Mile Creek and its 3 miles of private resident-only fly fishing. This newly updated cabin, and new large deck, with the Main level bedroom and en-suite has radiant floor heat all the way into the kitchen, where you’ll find new granite counters, new appliances and lighting. An open floor plan with a tongue and groove vaulted ceiling lets you enjoy the wood/pellet stove with your family and friends. The laundry room and a half bath are also on main level. There is an upper level large bedroom, full bath and loft that can be a sitting room or office, as well as lower level bedroom, full bath and bonus space, with radiant floor heat. Outside you’ll find 2 out buildings, consisting of 750 sq ft of garage space, and a 600 sq ft he/she shed! A perfect place for watching the stars at night and all the wildlife that wanders by.
